WEBVTT

1
00:32:20.691 --> 00:32:22.150
I'm here to pick up <i>Tu Polla</i>.

2
00:32:23.318 --> 00:32:24.319
Your dick.

3
00:35:45.312 --> 00:35:47.814
Hello. Ruben.

4
00:35:47.898 --> 00:35:51.193
You know who I am?

5
00:35:52.277 --> 00:35:57.199
Then you know this is
the last place I want to be.

6
00:35:58.867 --> 00:36:00.410
Then why are you here?

7
00:36:00.494 --> 00:36:04.498
I heard you were going to
drop your appeal.

8
00:36:06.542 --> 00:36:09.545
SJLP sent you.

9
00:36:09.628 --> 00:36:11.672
I told them I'm done.

10
00:36:13.549 --> 00:36:16.385
I came to tell you one thing...

11
00:36:16.468 --> 00:36:20.222
...that your pain has meaning.

12
00:36:20.973 --> 00:36:26.186
Your pain. you can embrace it
and turn it into strength.

13
00:36:47.332 --> 00:36:51.461
I never killed anyone
until they stuck me in this fucking place.

14
00:36:52.212 --> 00:36:55.215
This place gets to you!

15
00:36:55.299 --> 00:36:59.553
Just last week. I was right where you are.

16
00:37:00.345 --> 00:37:04.016
You think your story is over.
but it isn't.

17
00:37:05.767 --> 00:37:08.270
Maybe it isn't even your story.

18
00:37:08.353 --> 00:37:13.483
Maybe you have a much
greater purpose... underneath.

19
00:37:13.567 --> 00:37:15.903
Ruben!
